text: Dzhenko Sabev (2 June 1947 - 30 April 2020) was a Bulgarian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Bulgarian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Bulgaria Category:Equestrians at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
